# Rules

Always include a frontmatter when creating Jira files.

**title:** `[...]` it usualy is some ~3 letter abbreviation.

```format
---
title: [...] Ticket title
assigned: None
type: Task/Story/Epic
url: https://<atlassian-url>/NOVACORE-40565
status: todo/readyForDevelopment/inProgress/codeReview/
...more fields
---

[Markdown Ticket body]
```
